[00:00.748]Avicii - The Nights
[00:02.40]Lyrics by：Nicholas Furlong、Gabriel Benjamin、Jordan Suecof、John Feldmann、Tim Bergling、Ash Pournouri
[00:03.475]Composed by：Nicholas Furlong、Gabriel Benjamin、Jordan Suecof、John Feldmann、Tim Bergling、Ash Pournouri
[00:03.475]Once upon a younger year
[00:05.179]When all our shadows disappeared
[00:07.140]The animals inside came out to play
[00:10.855]When face to face with all our fears
[00:13.13]Learned our lessons through the tears
[00:14.619]Made memories we knew would never fade
[00:17.926]One day my father he told me
[00:20.17]Son don't let it slip away
[00:22.289]He took me in his arms I heard him say
[00:25.647]When you get older
[00:27.55]Your wild heart will live for younger days
[00:30.61]Think of me if ever you're afraid
[00:33.153]He said one day you'll leave this world behind
[00:36.997]So live a life you will remember
[00:40.846]My father told me when I was just a child
[00:44.623]These are the nights that never die
[00:48.21]My father told me
[01:19.513]When thunder clouds start pouring down
[01:21.557]Light a fire they can't put out
[01:23.489]Carve your name into those shining stars
